Return object with specific chains

Source: R/stan_retain.R
stan_retain.Rd

Use stan_retain() to choose chains to retain.

stan_retain(object, chains = 1)

Arguments

object

stanfit object
chains

numeric, chains to retain, Default: 1

Value

stanfit object

See also

Other utility: stan_axe(), stan_names()

Examples

rats <- rats_example(nCores = 1)

#retain first chain only
rats%>%
  stan_retain()
